I made this for a holiday gathering, and it was delicious and easy. I cooked the toppings and prepped the pizzas in the afternoon so that all I had to do was heat them up shortly before my guests arrived. This was an easy appetizer, and quite the crowd pleaser. I'm going to make this recipe again for my New Year's Eve party.

